name: GOD COMPLEXITY #4 - FOSSIL
description:
A series of visual experiments emerging from an attempt to simulate generative biological forms through geometry, collage and hand drawn animation. 

In this image, inspired in part by both @pointline_ & @arsiliath, a 3D animation of parametric geometry is re-staged in a 3D world to mimic a projection of a stack of self-occluding layers.

The result resembles an impression of prehistoric life, existing only in a fictional fossil record, with barely discernible elements of technological influence.
